If you have VS Code and the Live Server extension installed, you can follow the instructions below to run the project with live updates.

Once the index.html file is open, navigate through the website to test each page:

Index Page: This is the homepage where you can start.
Login Page: Click on the "Login" link to go to login.html and test the login functionality.
Account Overview: After logging in, you will be taken to account.html.
Payment Page: From the account overview, navigate to payment.html to test the payment submission.
Logout Page: Finally, click on the logout link to be taken to logout.html.
